      <title>瑞士冻结超过 140 亿美元的俄罗斯资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/switzerland-says-it-s-blocked-14-2-billion-of-russian-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士冻结了在该国持有的130亿瑞士法郎（143亿美元）的俄罗斯资产，其中包括俄罗斯央行超过70亿瑞士法郎的储备和资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/switzerland-says-it-s-blocked-14-2-billion-of-russian-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 07:10:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典 Alecta 在经历一年的动荡后实现正回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/sweden-s-alecta-posts-positive-returns-after-year-of-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典养老基金 Alecta 宣布利基银行和房地产损失超过 30 亿美元一年后，其投资获得了丰厚的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/sweden-s-alecta-posts-positive-returns-after-year-of-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 07:02:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国钢铁出口激增加剧全球贸易紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/china-s-surging-steel-exports-are-inflaming-global-trade-tension</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着金属到达更广泛的目的地，中国自2010年代中期全球供应过剩以来最大规模的钢铁出口浪潮正在加剧世界各地的贸易紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/china-s-surging-steel-exports-are-inflaming-global-trade-tension</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 06:59:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国今年计划的金边债券销售量增幅超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/uk-raises-planned-gilt-sales-for-year-by-more-than-expected</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府增加了本财年计划出售的债券数量，增幅超过分析师预期，这已经是有记录以来第二大的英国国债计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/uk-raises-planned-gilt-sales-for-year-by-more-than-expected</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 06:45:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英美资源集团在复苏缓慢之际削减钻石产量目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/anglo-american-cuts-diamond-output-goal-amid-slow-recovery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc) 削减了今年的钻石产量目标，因为该行业在经历了灾难性的 2023 年之后，仍继续面临库存过多的困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/anglo-american-cuts-diamond-output-goal-amid-slow-recovery</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 06:13:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雷诺强劲的电动汽车价格和较低的成本有助于抵消需求下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/renault-beats-revenue-estimates-on-clio-megane-e-tech-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管竞争对手受到电动汽车市场放缓的影响，但由于对电动梅甘娜 E-Tech 等一系列车型的持续需求，雷诺公司受益于稳健的定价和成本控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/renault-beats-revenue-estimates-on-clio-megane-e-tech-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 05:00:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市收益上涨，美国期货持平：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对大型科技公司本周将带来强劲盈利的乐观情绪，欧洲股市连续第二天上涨，追随亚洲市场的上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 22:31:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国杂货商阿斯达寻求通过新贷款和债券解决债务墙问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/asda-begins-tackling-debt-pile-with-new-1-05-billion-term-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，阿斯达集团有限公司正计划发行债券和贷款，以帮助为加油站企业家 Mohsin 和 Zuber Issa 收购该公司的债务进行再融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/asda-begins-tackling-debt-pile-with-new-1-05-billion-term-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 14:53:43 GMT</pubDate>
